----------------------------------------
author : Kartik - Gupta
topic : How to build the magic_creatar.cpp library (libmagic.so declared in "Android.mk")

----------------------------------------


It requires the github repo of artoolkit5 
In that 
1) goto AndroidStudioProjects / kModfiedProjects / CreatNewLibProject / 
2) goto sample lib ...it contains the same jni folder as here
3)go inside that folder in terminal and run "ndk-build"
